Package: evidenceguide
Type: Package
Title: Client for the Evidence Guide API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Evidence Guide",
           family = "Team",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "support@evidence.guide")
Description: Provides a thin client over the Evidence Guide API for uploading PDF
    articles, polling for processing status, and exporting study-level data in
    tidy format suitable for meta-analytic workflows.
